        <Parent_String>Early Byzantine [300106792], Byzantine (culture and style) [300020669], Early Christian-Byzantine styles, cultures, periods [300020658], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
